{"tid":2022122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家應該多謝建制派加入攬炒大軍！","createTime":"2020-05-18T06:45:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T08:42:03.000Z","uid":14256,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7e24590b16e6abafa128b819543786c00f7b9f9c","tid":2022122,"uid":14256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T06:45:22.000Z","msg":"點解咁講？<br />\n<br />\n1. 攬炒派其中一大戰線就係國際線，如果港共同建制派唔做柒事出醜，我地twitter點推都無用。所以今次暴力強搶內會主席一職，成功引起所羅門等人關注，建制派應記一功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 攬炒既元素就係使大家無退路，硬碰硬。今次成功令黃碧雲有零的突破，係建制攬炒直接逼使黃碧雲再進化，可喜可賀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 建制成功令大家回憶起上年議會雙胞胎，為左迎接即將來臨既反送中行動一週年而炒熱大家既氣氛，令到一眾泛民人士無需費煞思量如何吸引大眾既視線，實為明智之舉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以大家，請盡情歡迎建制派加入我地攬炒陣型 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"299e0e4c89d52a40250e54d887045544771cf0a9","tid":2022122,"uid":21028,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T06:47:01.000Z","msg":"議會咁嘅情況 令人擔憂<br />\n應斷關係法"},{"pid":"72a7762e476d5199e0be0b6d5f5c2a455c83c3ac","tid":2022122,"uid":14256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"299e0e4c89d52a40250e54d887045544771cf0a9","tid":2022122,"uid":21028,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T06:47:01.000Z","msg":"議會咁嘅情況 令人擔憂<br />\n應斷關係法"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T06:48:37.000Z","msg":"咁我地既攬炒大計咪開始成功囉<br />\n<br />\n建制派議員應記一功 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"461e0d7a9bcc23363b87a904551054db96788617","tid":2022122,"uid":14256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T06:51:10.000Z","msg":"我地應該大肆宣揚建制派加入攬炒陣營既利好消息 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86ccb